: \"the 13-race qualifying series\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 916}, {\"ngram\": \"the Mediterranean\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 937}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Want more?Here's the full list of all our Olympics stories That meant he moved straight into the final, awaiting his two competitors.\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 1093, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the full list\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 989}, {\"ngram\": \"all our Olympics stories\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1017}, {\"ngram\": \"his two competitors\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1091}]}, {\"sentence\": \"World champion van Opzeeland won the quarter-final and semi-final earlier on Saturday with Reuveny, who was ranked second from qualifying, finishing second.\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1251, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"World champion van Opzeeland\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1123}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday\", \"from\": 1172, \"to\": 1180}, {\"ngram\": \"Reuveny\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1193}, {\"ngram\": \"qualifying\", \"from\": 1222, \"to\": 1232}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the sailors were recalled for a second start, racing in the final got underway in perfect, top-end wind.\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1363, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sailors\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1270}, {\"ngram\": \"a second start\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1303}, {\"ngram\": \"perfect, top-end wind\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1362}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In iQFOiL windsurfing, the sailors fly off the water at high speed, the boards lifted by a foil with athletes pushing speeds well above 20 knots (37 kilometres per hour).\", \"from\": 1365, \"to\": 1535, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"iQFOiL windsurfing\", \"from\": 1368, \"to\": 1386}, {\"ngram\": \"the sailors\", \"from\": 1388, \"to\": 1399}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1417}, {\"ngram\": \"high speed\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1431}, {\"ngram\": \"the boards\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1443